<br>
And, none of the other travelers I had ever seen, knew what they were either.  Now, the other denizens, animals, and natives to the area were a hearty lot; so it reasons that heretics would be as well.<br>
<br>
So, it is my learned conclusion then that there are three things to be learned from this.<br>
<br>
1) Heretics are, most likely, a very rare creature<br>
